Maps an `Option<&T>` to an `Option<T>` by copying the contents of the
option.

# Examples

```
let x = 12;
let opt_x = Some(&x);
assert_eq!(opt_x, Some(&12));
let copied = opt_x.copied();
assert_eq!(copied, Some(12));
```
